{"tid":312472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"搭巴士坐上層","createTime":"2017-07-07T12:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T08:08:17.000Z","uid":126981,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"549188c6ae2aee1ec8800b87493d836ec40ca5a3","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我住新界, 每朝搭過海巴士返工<br />\n今朝上車行上巴士上層<br />\n見到坐部近窗位既都坐晒<br />\n得返走"},{"pid":"3d07cada9fda924f718734bec0b7f9abdacf0197","tid":312472,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"79b6781a08ad7c0679f3f3d193a69001fe5e138e","tid":312472,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"唔識趕人走？"},{"pid":"c3a321471dd37fb9241142b17a69673057df85fb","tid":312472,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"大叫真主萬歲，之後再係袋𥚃攞D誠意出黎，咁都冇窗口位坐我切！"},{"pid":"feb7c601562a937793bbfa296cb0ad9ec7c272f0","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n我住新界, 每朝搭過海巴士返工<br />\n今朝上車行上巴士上層<br />\n見到坐部近窗位既都坐晒<br />\n得返走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry未打晒就㩒錯制出左post<br />\n由頭講過先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n我住新界, 每朝搭過海巴士返工<br />\n今朝上車行上巴士上層<br />\n見到全部近窗位既都坐晒<br />\n得返走廊位, 咁就是但啦<br />\n揀左坐係個OL隔離<br />\n<br />\n咁去到港島, 就開始多人落車啦<br />\n就會有D冇人坐既孖位出現返<br />\n而我又未有咁快落車<br />\n坐我隔離個OL又未落車<br />\n<br />\n如果係你既話<br />\n你會坐返係原本個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係轉過去坐冇人坐緊既孖位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n我最尾係照坐返原本個位<br />\n之後越黎越多孖位出現返<br />\n但隔離個OL都係未落車<br />\n個情況就變左成車好多吉位但我地又坐埋一齊咁<br />\n唔知點解覺得怪怪地<br />\n但又冇理由過左幾個站先突然間轉位架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89877c1813efd7ac9435f4a5cae161ef7e1095e1","tid":312472,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8ff57d65b74061bf15052155dd4b25fe85ba4e4","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的<br />\n我住新界, 每朝搭過海巴士返工<br />\n今朝上車行上巴士上層<br />\n見到坐部近窗位既都坐晒<br />\n得返走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry未打晒就㩒錯制出左post<br />\n由頭講過先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n我住新界, 每朝搭過海巴士返工<br />\n今朝上車行上巴士上層<br />\n見到全部近窗位既都坐晒<br />\n得返走廊位, 咁就是但啦<br />\n揀左坐係個OL隔離<br />\n<br />\n咁去到港島, 就開始多人落車啦<br />\n就會有D冇人坐既孖位出現返<br />\n而我又未有咁快落車<br />\n坐我隔離個OL又未落車<br />\n<br />\n如果係你既話<br />\n你會坐返係原本個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係轉過去坐冇人坐緊既孖位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n我最尾係照坐返原本個位<br />\n之後越黎越多孖位出現返<br />\n但隔離個OL都係未落車<br />\n個情況就變左成車好多吉位但我地又坐埋一齊咁<br />\n唔知點解覺得怪怪地<br />\n但又冇理由過左幾個站先突然間轉位架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係OL就扮落車，其實自己坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢又冇喎仲咁岩同我同一個站落車<br />\n都唔知佢點諗我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能由上車果一刻已經唔想我坐佢隔離啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028e0d5272281c3f4303c0cbd5cfaf259fe73cc6","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry巴打我未打晒就出左<br />\n有update出左"},{"pid":"ef7fb6b283a644a8a27f5c873fd6759390a038f5","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識趕人走？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒撚講野都唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de98173d4a62c460bb4d47b47b106a6ed12d361","tid":312472,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60b5ccd0e398798720d8e0bb7a4b183a2a9916bd","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大叫真主萬歲，之後再係袋𥚃攞D誠意出黎，咁都冇窗口位坐我切！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n攞D誠意即係咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6704667465b87bfaee0942a0b56147e6e087714","tid":312472,"uid":60412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"如果你樣衰最好快d坐開<br />\n如果靚仔就坐耐d都冇問題"},{"pid":"8a736b965bc65b5a80de20459d2363ed38aa4ca1","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無坐到大脾貼大脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢著住條短裙真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上到去揀位果陣唔知架<br />\n坐低左先留意到<br />\n冇啦點敢掂人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d8149a96c5a768eeeeb4ebb139823ef0258bf5","tid":312472,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"056bac674ba966d6c845da3c617574357dc5de80","tid":312472,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"巴打唔洗諗咁多<br />\n只要你正正常常唔係咸咸濕濕咁<br />\n其實冇乜嘢<br />\n因為唔係成架車好空個陣 你揀咗坐佢隔離<br />\n所以架車空個陣 冇換位坐好平常"},{"pid":"1d77bd356e200e1d107b5b554f178af080c10a6e","tid":312472,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"一向唔理隔離咩人 總之有孖位就會直接轉位"},{"pid":"30dd9ce779e9610e078d6bc3fd456ca6d86d4136","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你樣衰最好快d坐開<br />\n如果靚仔就坐耐d都冇問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果樣子一般既話呢?<br />\n唔係講緊我, 根據你咁講我下次會坐開架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d2261586ea8a14aeffedce117b2ab389343428","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你樣衰最好快d坐開<br />\n如果靚仔就坐耐d都冇問題</blockquote><br />\nx2<br />\n樣好靚，身型好，就咩都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靚仔有型真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805122f036e127eb410c15841787953b2827c0b6","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打唔洗諗咁多<br />\n只要你正正常常唔係咸咸濕濕咁<br />\n其實冇乜嘢<br />\n因為唔係成架車好空個陣 你揀咗坐佢隔離<br />\n所以架車空個陣 冇換位坐好平常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果陣都係諗住坐開就費事轉位<br />\n點知去到果一刻覺得好似怪怪地<br />\n聽你咁講好似都係好正常冇咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd1fa1f7b614af4925f5dd490ea033980e10407","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一向唔理隔離咩人 總之有孖位就會直接轉位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有諗過<br />\n如果我見有孖位就即轉走<br />\n個OL會唔會覺得我好似好唔想同佢坐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有巴打都講係睇樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce2f00b57f8408fdd4fdb57c9d71ef983205b2b","tid":312472,"uid":37005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"我會繼續坐原位 除非拎住好多嘢或者坐得唔舒服<br />\n我會覺得即刻走開坐空位好似好冇禮貌<br />\n不過一般正正常常唔係過肥或者有體味繼續坐都冇咩問題嘅 樓主唔使過份擔心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a7e0374d9686e9320a460a8cea572567654932","tid":312472,"uid":22949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一向唔理隔離咩人 總之有孖位就會直接轉位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有諗過<br />\n如果我見有孖位就即轉走<br />\n個OL會唔會覺得我好似好唔想同佢坐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有巴打都講係睇樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你竟然會產生個OL想你坐係佢隔離嘅錯覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7983d52df42d813ecc610bea7139ea610d168b05","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會繼續坐原位 除非拎住好多嘢或者坐得唔舒服<br />\n我會覺得即刻走開坐空位好似好冇禮貌<br />\n不過一般正正常常唔係過肥或者有體味繼續坐都冇咩問題嘅 樓主唔使過份擔心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀係呀 情況就係唔知人地點諗<br />\n如果佢係嫌棄我既話我留係度就唔好<br />\n但如果佢唔嫌棄我既話我走左就好冇禮貌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難捉摸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516b44d07aff947831480d8b8a608ae870eccbbf","tid":312472,"uid":55907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會繼續坐原位 除非拎住好多嘢或者坐得唔舒服<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我會覺得即刻走開坐空位好似好冇禮貌</span><br />\n不過一般正正常常唔係過肥或者有體味繼續坐都冇咩問題嘅 樓主唔使過份擔心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅字agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab2926610ee68acc2deeda2dd3062e5120629ff","tid":312472,"uid":55907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我會繼續坐原位 除非拎住好多嘢或者坐得唔舒服<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我會覺得即刻走開坐空位好似好冇禮貌</span><br />\n不過一般正正常常唔係過肥或者有體味繼續坐都冇咩問題嘅 樓主唔使過份擔心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅字agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會覺得即刻走開坐空位好似好冇禮貌<br />\n<br />\nagger呢句"},{"pid":"11e571893ed4a60ddf39293369d6946284f8784b","tid":312472,"uid":126981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一向唔理隔離咩人 總之有孖位就會直